title: Hispanic coalition: Take Trump off 'Saturday Night Live' - WKXW-FM Trenton
text:
AUGUST 25: Donald Trump at a campaign event at the Grand River Center on August 25, 2015 in Dubuque, Iowa. In a letter sent Thursday to the show's producer and the CEO of NBC Universal, the National Hispanic Leadership Agenda said the network was enabling Trump's "hateful speech" in exchange for ratings.
 WKXW-FM Trenton.
